{"tid":1100972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[休班警]  羅湖過境藏毒被捕","createTime":"2019-04-10T18:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T00:48:17.000Z","uid":123082,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"774e347ce0c057db40e13ad14fd953bc037b1e72","tid":1100972,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T18:30:31.000Z","msg":"西九龍交通部一名休班警員，本周一經羅湖管制站由深圳返港時，被海關人員在其身上及行李搜獲0.8克冰毒、一個冰壼及238支未完稅香煙。<br />\n<br />\n該名警員46歲，他涉嫌藏毒、藏有可作吸食毒品工具及藏有應課稅貨品被捕，被帶返海關調查後，獲准保釋候查；而涉事警員在被海關拘捕後，已被警方停職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190410&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59474317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190410%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59474317&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=1e5ea7f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190410%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59474317&h=64bdeb71\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190410&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59474317</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地冇錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係佔中既錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n海關竟然唔體諒警務人員壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208fe5d809a703fb8f269ec0e7c5e94092dafc08","tid":1100972,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T18:36:57.000Z","msg":"有牌爛仔係咁上下"},{"pid":"df0e17eaa11208a03fc31874d471678e3450452f","tid":1100972,"uid":246419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T19:42:31.000Z","msg":"自己人都拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地冇做錯到"},{"pid":"1f50102c0c33f0ec5d2fbb493e9d1424b41da21b","tid":1100972,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"